1 modify data/Xsession as your distribution
It can run under fedora now, but may can't run on your system, for packagers, follow next steps may help

find Xsession on your system, remember it as OS_XSESSION
set the content of data/Xsession with

############################################################
#!/bin/bash

if [ $# -eq 1 ]; then
        LXSESSION=$1
else
        LXSESSION=/usr/bin/startlxde
fi

OS_XSESSION=/etc/X11/xinit/Xsession

exec OS_XSESSION $LXSESSION
#############################################################

of cource you should replace OS_XSESSION with yours

2 compile and install

./configure --prefix=/usr
make
make install

